🎁 In the holiday spirit, I'm treating 2 people to rest, reconnect, and recharge with an @AIREMbeautyrituals Ritual Box! 🎁 This gift set includes a tea ritual and healing @AIREMessentials skincare routine for two to experience gwallee at home, the Korean term for self-care. Nominate someone who could use a break this hectic holiday season by tagging them in the comments – I will be picking two tagged people on Sunday night. (FYI: the nominee must live in the US, so we can ship it to them!)

🫖 The Ritual Box includes: Canvas Hyaluronic Cleanser, 2 × Pearlessence Face Mask, Cocoon Healing Balm, Tea Set for Two, AIREM Signature White Lotus Tea, and step-by-step instructions on how to host your own meditative tea ceremony. 
🎬 Make sure to watch the AIREM by BBC Storyworks Commercial Production "In Pursuit of Wellness" film at bit.ly/airemfilm to learn why finding ways to slow down, quieting your mind, and replenishing your wellbeing through the self-care rituals (like the ones found in this gift box!) are so important to me as a busy mom of 3, facial plastic surgeon, and business owner.

1 day after #PlasmaTite Neck @airembeautyrituals non-surgical neck lift. Tightening,contouring, sculpting and defining. Taking you through my patient’s journey as she gets ready for her son’s wedding. Results only 1 day after her #plasmaTite minimally invasive neck contouring treatment done while she was awake. There are so many variables that go into which procedure is best. Facelift and neck lift is the gold standard but aesthetic innovation is paving the way for exciting technology that enhances the results of a non-surgical neck lift.  @renuvion @renuvion_newyork @renuvion_ryan

Celebrating Korean-American heritage @kacfny gala and the amazing work they do to support numerous #AAPI initiatives across the city and the country.

Creating programs that address these needs require funding and @airembeautyrituals is proud to be a sponsor of the @kacfny gala.

Family travel to Korea can be…..challenging. This summer my kids got to visit Korea 🇰🇷 for the first time! Navigated Seoul as a family of 5 + 2 grandparents + our BFF family of 4 = 11 people + other friends we met with along the way. Experiencing Korea through my kids opened up a whole new world of wonder and fascination for me. 💫

Home base:  @oakwoodpremierseoul - The suites are spacious, has a full kitchen, washer/dryer unit and most importantly connected underground to the entire Coex, Parnas, Intercontinental and Hyundai department store network. You don’t have to step outside in monsoon/humid/sweltering weather to have access to hundreds of stores/restaurants and fun things to do for kids - including the @coex_aquarium and @megaboxon movie theater.   App:  MUST download the Kakao Taxi app @kakaot_official. There’s some confusion that foreigners (a common term for Non-Korean nationals) can’t use this app but you CAN! It is critical for getting around Seoul and you can request a larger car (minivan) with this app too. Works in Busan and Jeju as well!   Value:  Discover Seoul Pass @discoverseoulpass_en provides access to so many different attractions. Can choose between 24hr, 48hr and 72hr access. Our family favorites include @happylotteworld, hanbok experience at Changdeokgung Palace, @coex_aquarium and numerous museums throughout Seoul. 

 #familytravel #korea #seoul #familytraveltips #workingmomlife

Merz Expert Summit #MEXS in📍Barcelona, Spain. Thank you @merzaesthetics for the invitation to learn and collaborate with global aesthetic leaders. Physicians from all across the world - from Thailand to Brazil to the Middle East, South Africa and the Americas - sharing innovative treatment protocols for beautiful and natural results that enhance the confidence of our patients. 

The future of aesthetics lies in 
➡️ Combination treatments incorporating neuromodulator + biostimulator + energy devices that push the boundaries of non-surgical skin tightening and lifting. 

➡️ Regenerative aesthetics - the use of biostimulators to enhance and boost collagen formation to smooth and contour the skin. 

➡️ Global aesthetic community - doctors no longer have to practice in silos. A global network allows doctors to collaborate, share data and develop best practices to achieve the best outcomes for our patients. 

Merz 4 Cs #Courage #Commitment #Collaboration #Confidence
